    incant is a computer language with flexible syntax and the ability to extend itself.
    Its grammar is similar to Python, however, unlike Python, incant is designed
    to define itself and write itself. For now, incant can be extended in incant;
    in future, the plan is incant will be written in incant from GO to whoa.
    The basic idea is: turn incant into an ouroboros (maybe phoenix is a better
    analogy) language able to regenerate itself. The bottom line is: if you do not
